--====================================================================
--  VISUAL TRADE SPAWNER  --  LocalScript (client-side only)
--====================================================================
--  Put this in a LocalScript (e.g. StarterPlayer > StarterPlayerScripts).
--
--  PURELY VISUAL. It only edits GUI on the client running it. Nothing
--  is replicated to the server or other players. No executor functions.
--
--  Behaviour:
--    * the "Gears" side button's Txt is renamed to "Gears + Gamepasses"
--    * spawned cards are shown ONLY while that button is green
--    * the real trade selection slots are left untouched
